# Cloudflare Pages redirects
#
# NOTE for Cloudflare (not Netlify):
#   - No "!" force flag (Cloudflare reads "301!" as an invalid status).
#   - Only RELATIVE destinations allowed (no absolute https://… URLs).
#   - SPA fallback is handled by wrangler "not_found_handling: single-page-application",
#     so NO "/* /index.html 200" line here (it triggers a loop error).
#   - Host-level redirects (www -> apex, http -> https) are handled at the
#     Cloudflare platform level: "Always Use HTTPS" + a www->apex Redirect Rule.

# Case sensitivity (legacy capitalized paths)
/Projects /projects 301
/Blog /blog 301
/Contact /contact 301
/Tech-Stack /tech-stack 301
/Faq /faq 301
/Privacy-Policy /privacy-policy 301

# Old tech-stack URLs -> current slugs
/tech-stack/security /tech-stack/cybersecurity-practices 301
/tech-stack/backend /tech-stack/code-engineering 301
/tech-stack/frontend /tech-stack/nocode-solutions 301
/tech-stack/tools /tech-stack/optimization-maintenance 301
